channel.title: Skys Shadow's Edgevlle Yew Cutter 2.0
channel.description: After awhile away from SCAR scripting, I have redone a lot of my Edgeville Yew Cutter. However, I have a limited amount of time and would like it if some people could help me test it. Some current bugs that I am trying to fix are walking outside of the yew building, and missing the tree when trying to click. If you could post any other errors and if you somehow get a progress report then post that also. Thanks in advance to anyone who helps. Script is attached.
